original: Ekman, Tage, tandläkare, Halmstad, f. 17/12/94 i Halmstad av Hjalmar E. o. Charlotte Wulff. G. m. Rosa Brei-mer. Barn: Nina f. 35. — Stud:ex. i Halmstad 15, tandl :kand. 17, tandl. 19. Prakt, i Piteå 19-31, i Halmstad sed. 31. Hobbies: jakt o. fiske.
translated: Ekman, Tage, dentist, Halmstad, b. December 17, 1894 in Halmstad to Hjalmar E. and Charlotte Wulff. Married to Rosa Brei-mer in an unknown year. Children: Nina b. 1935. Studied at Halmstad high school in 1915, dental school in 1917, and graduated as a dentist in 1919. Practiced in Piteå from 1919 to 1931, then returned to Halmstad. Hobbies include hunting and fishing.
